Domino’s Pizza Nigeria has launched Mobile App  for its customers and also offering  a whopping 50% discount on every medium-sized classic pizza ordered via the app.  This time, it’s with the launch of a mobile app tailored for Nigerians and  It’s better, faster, and easy to use. Not only that, the consumers also enjoy first-hand information on special deals, promos and discounts via the New push notification feature.  Simply visit your Google Play or Apple Stores to join the happy users enjoying these delectable offerings. You can also scan this QR code which is also available across all their stores, social media pages for easy download. You sure don’t want to miss out on this amazing offering to satisfy your pizza cravings. With only a few clicks you can enjoy all of the delicious, hot, spicy, sweet and cheesy Domino’s Pizza with a mix of delightful toppings, made just for you. Imagine having access to all of your favourite flavour in your pocket, your own store in your pocket if you will. Satisfy all your pizza cravings with insane slashed prices! Who is like us and ready to download this app to enjoy the amazing deals and  app is available to both Android & iOS.